  <brief_title>Comparison of Respiratory Muscle, Pain, Functional Performance and Cognitive Status in Obstructive Lung Diseases</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of Cognitive Status, Pain, Functional Status, Postural Awareness, Respiratory Muscle Strength and Endurance in Obstructive Pulmonary Diseases</official_title>
