  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In the literature, there are a limited number of studies evaluating postural awareness,&#xD;
      cognitive status, respiratory muscle strength and endurance, functional capacity, and pain in&#xD;
      people with obstructive pulmonary disease, and comparing these parameters with each other and&#xD;
      with healthy subjects, and most of the studies are on chronic obstructive pulmonary disease&#xD;
      patients. There we will evaluate these parameters in different obstructive lung diseases and&#xD;
      compare the findings of healthy individuals.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
